text.__SUMMARY__: Matudaea trinervia is a species of plant in the Hamamelidaceae family. It is endemic to Mexico.
text.Sources: González-Espinosa, M. (1998). "Matudaea trinervia". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 1998: e.T34414A9865750. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T34414A9865750.en. Retrieved 21 December 2017.
